{"type":null,"faqId":48071,"title":"日历","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>日历方便您管理日常生活和工作中的各项活动，例如提前安排日常计划、查阅节假日信息。当联系人中存有生日信息时，日历还会自动创建生日提醒。</span><a name=\"_task_add_event-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">新建活动</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"创建日历活动\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178060\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178061\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>输入活动标题、开始及结束时间、重复周期及活动地点等详细信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178062\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span><a name=\"_task_check_event-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">查看日历</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"月视图\"XE \"日视图\"XE \"年视图\"XE \"查看节假日\"XE \"查看活动\"XE \"特定日期\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178063\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.在“日历”界面，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击“月”、“周”、“日”，在月视图、周视图和日视图中进行切换。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>在月视图、周视图和日视图中，左右滑动屏幕在不同月份、星期和日期间切换。</span><a name=\"_task_view_global_holiday-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">查看全球节假日</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"查看各国节假日\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178064\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178065\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 要显示的日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“全球节假日”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.点击要查看国家旁边的开关，手机会自动连接网络下载节假日信息。</span><a name=\"_task_set_local_calendar-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">设置本地历法</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"本地历法\"XE \"设置伊斯兰历\"XE \"设置佛历\"XE \"设置波斯历\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178066\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178067\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 要显示的日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“本地历法”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.选择一种本地历法，手机会自动下载历法的相关信息。</span><a name=\"_task_set_sync_display-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">同步日历</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"日历同步\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178068\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178069\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 要显示的日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.打开要显示的日历帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178070\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 要同步的日历”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5.选择要同步日历的帐户，开启同步。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3657","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Convenient-features","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598110000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":51,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}